ğŸ—‚ STEP 2: PREPARE DAILY TASK PLAN (external)

Cursor doesn't read .md files â€” you paste each task into the agent queue.
Example:

## Agent: analytics-ui-agent

1. Create /analytics React page  
2. Add chart props and dummy bar chart  
