### JOURNAL
1. Read docs/agent-log.md (create if missing)
2. Append:

## <AGENT_NAME> â€“ <YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM>
- Scope: <high-level goal>
- Key files touched: <list>
- Tests: âœ… or âŒ
- Preview: <url>
